--- !u!114 &2684024005323760421
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1311249835568238718}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7e92d96f9fecb904e8b124d518518b03, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  initialConversation:
  - speakerName: Little Kid
    text: Ms. Cafeteria Lady, I told you, my change is short!
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f229f236d3ba1834f9ef5ba69e814df8, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: I'm sorry, but I just can't believe that. The machine spat that out!
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Little Kid
    text: But I recomputed everything, I was short!
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f229f236d3ba1834f9ef5ba69e814df8, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: Hmm, how can we solve this...
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: Ah! Detective! I didn't see you there.
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: 'You''re a trustworthy person who knows how to compute for percentages
      and increases, right? '
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: Would you mind recomputing the receipt that the machine printed? I'm sure
      it's right.
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: Speaking of, where is it, little girl?
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Little Kid
    text: "I left the food and receipt over by a poster, and I\u2019m sure there\u2019s
      a trash can nearby too."
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f229f236d3ba1834f9ef5ba69e814df8, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: Hmm, I see. Detective, would you mind checking that receipt and recomputing
      the math for us? Thank you!
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Little Kid
    text: Please help, detective!
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f229f236d3ba1834f9ef5ba69e814df8, type: 3}
  solvedConversation:
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: So how did it go, Detective? Are we now certain that the machine is right?
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Little Kid
    text: Please Detective, I recomputed everything! I just learned about percentages
      in my math class recently, and I know I'm right!
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f229f236d3ba1834f9ef5ba69e814df8, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Detective
    text: Ms. Cafeteria Lady, how much exactly did you give this little kid?
    voiceLine: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: 'Well, she gave me {amountGiven}, and I gave her {wrongChange}... and that''s
      after the added tax! '
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Detective
    text: Ms. Cafeteria Lady, I recomputed everything, and the change you're supposed
      to give is {change}, and yes, that's after added tax.
    voiceLine: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Detective
    text: It's exactly what the machine printed, too. I'm sure it's just a mistake
      on your part.
    voiceLine: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: Oh.....! I see... I'm sorry little kid, I'll give you the change you need.
      I guess I read the receipt wrong? Ehehe...
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Little Kid
    text: Thank you, Ms.! It's okay, we all make mistakes. and thank you too, Detective!
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f229f236d3ba1834f9ef5ba69e814df8, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Cafeteria Lady
    text: Yes, thank you detective! Without your help, this problem wouldn't be solved.
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 01b56d40ecad0054aa787575336c6fcc, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Detective
    text: All in a day's work.
    voiceLine: {fileID: 0}
  hintConversation:
  - speakerName: Detective
    text: Hmm, they told me I should recompute the receipt to check for errors. The
      little kid mentioned its by a poster, near a trash can. I should get to work.
    voiceLine: {fileID: 0}
